  vlc-9999.ebuild:
  Made USE="vaapi" depend on virtual/ffmpeg[vaapi] as that is needed for GPU
  accelerated decoding; fixes bug #430960 reported by James and dolohow, with
  the help of Alexis Ballier (aballier).

